header.header
  .container-fluid
    button.btn.btn-link.header__toggler(ng-click="sidebar.toggle(false)")
      i.fa.fa-bars.fa-2x
      span.sr-only Ouvrir le menu
    .row.text-center
      .col-xs-5
        //- Silence is golden
      .col-xs-2.header__logo
        a(href="http://www.rts.ch/info/", target="_blank")
          img(src="assets/images/rts-red.svg", height="40px")
      .col-xs-5
        .header__share.pull-right
          a(ng-click="sharer.tw()")
            i.fa.fa-twitter
          a(ng-click="sharer.fb()")
            i.fa.fa-facebook
        .text-right.text-muted.lead.header__hashtag
          | <strong>#parlometre</strong> sur Twitter et Facebook
